sect1.title: External Interfaces
sect1.para: The external interfaces are represented by the generated RTE based on the DWA_SstSr.xml sst file. DWA_SstSr.xml is exported from DWA_SST.xlsx with the mapping set in the DWA_SstSr.xsd file.

DWA_SST.xlsx location: https://eu.artifactory.conti.de/artifactory/i_bs_vw_meb_19_icas1_chorus_packages_conan_releases_l/appl/ZV_Lib DWA_SstSr.xsd location: https://github-vni.geo.conti.de/bs-vw-meb-19-icas1-chorus/sw.sys.chorus_main_doc/blob/master/mc_sw/appl/ZV_Lib/DWA/Evo/cfg/rteCfg/xsd/DWA_SstSr.xsd DWA_SstSr.xml location: https://github-vni.geo.conti.de/bs-vw-meb-19-icas1-chorus/sw.sys.chorus_main_doc/blob/master/mc_sw/appl/ZV_Lib/DWA/Evo/cfg/rteLight/mirror/DWA_SstSr.xml

sect1.title: External Dependencies
sect1.para: The external dependencies of the component are the library functions (cyclic_dwa()).
